The '''Victorian Major Events Company''' is a foundation for [[sport]]ing and [[Culture|cultural]] events in [[Melbourne, Victoria]], [[Australia]]. The corporation was founded in 1991 as part of a Victorian Government initiative to attract international cultural and sporting events that require global state-of-the-art facilities and infrastructure.<ref>[http://www.vmec.com.au/mission.html The VMEC]; last accessed May 26, 2011</ref>

